<subSubSection pageId="52" pageNumber="810" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="52.[788,1382,395,818]" pageId="52" pageNumber="810">
Based on genetic data, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Harrison" baseAuthorityYear="1979" box="[1146,1381,509,542]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="arabicus">Hypsugo arabicus</taxonomicName>
appears to be sister to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Bonaparte" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[1098,1201,548,581]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="savii">H. savii</taxonomicName>
, with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[1283,1382,548,581]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ariel">H. ariel</taxonomicName>
basal to this clade. Often placed in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kaup" authorityYear="1829" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pipistrellus</taxonomicName>
, but genetic data unequivocally situate this species in 
<taxonomicName box="[1042,1153,666,699]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsugo</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
